About Me

Hi, I’m Zainab — a frontend developer with a dream to build things that feel alive on the web. From smooth animations to responsive layouts, I love turning creative ideas into beautiful code.

I started my journey during my O-Levels, juggling school and self-learning in the late hours. With curiosity as my compass, I dived deep into React, Next.js, and everything that powers the modern web.

My portfolio is a reflection of my belief that websites should not just **work** — they should **feel**. Feel inspiring, personal, and magical. Just like this one ✨

When I’m not coding, you’ll find me exploring UI/UX designs, watching tech videos, or imagining my next big project. I'm a proud dream chaser — and this portfolio is just the beginning of my story.

My Skills

  • React.js
  • Next.js
  • HTML / CSS / JavaScript
  • TypeScript
  • Git & GitHub
  • Figma
  • ShadCN UI
